00:13:16.810 --> 00:13:18.830
figuring out what
you can just ignore

00:13:18.830 --> 00:13:20.930
and what you have
to definitely do,

00:13:20.930 --> 00:13:23.160
and then some the
psychology stuff related

00:13:23.160 --> 00:13:25.020
